        Creates an vAPI client that uses HTTP connection.
        Parameters:
        uri - URI representing the server to connect. Should be of the form http(s)://[IP_address]:[port]/[Service_endpoint]. Can not be null.
        clientConfig - the client configuration. can be null.
        httpConfig - the transport configuration. can be null.
